Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.03,0:21:59.57,Dragon Ball 3,,0,0,0,, {\i1}¡No escondas tu juventud!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.57,0:22:02.58,Dragon Ball 2,,0,0,0,, {\i1}Fushigi shitakute{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.57,0:22:02.58,Dragon Ball 3,,0,0,0,, {\i1}Quiero hacer lo misterioso{\i0}
